pageContext.claim: “More than one million Americans have already received the China Virus Vaccine, a record pace!”
pageContext.analysis: During his re-election campaign, Trump repeatedly promised 100 million doses of a coronavirus vaccine would be delivered by the end of 2020. But that turned out to be false. The Trump administration was heavily criticized for its faulty rollout, which allowed only about 12 million doses to be distributed by the end of the year.
